---
title: Golden Fried Tofu with Curried Veggies and Basmati Rice
description: A delightful meal courtesy of lightly dredged and fried tofu.  Veggies braised in a light curry sauce adorn fragrant rice for a pairing made in dinnertime heaven.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-poele-dore-0147dc2d.jpg
